# --- Monorepo: factory-digital-twin / factory-ops / visionguard folded in 2026-06-19 ---
# Each sub-dir keeps its own nested .gitignore (git honors those); the lines below are
# a backstop for heavy / generated / regenerable artifacts across the three.

# Generated data & model artifacts (large, regenerable)
**/synthetic-images/output/
**/events.jsonl
**/model-training/data/
**/model-training/models/
**/inference-server/models/*.onnx
**/inference-server/models/*.pt
**/runs/
**/minio-data/

# Python envs / caches
**/.venv/
**/venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.egg-info/
.ruff_cache/

# Node / Next
**/node_modules/
**/.next/

# Go build output
factory-ops/gateway/gateway

# Secrets — never commit
**/.env
**/.env.local
*.pem
*.key

# Local tooling / misc
.claude/settings.local.json
*.log
.DS_Store
